body:
MCVE is as follows:

```
module main;
    logic [7*8-1:0] s;
    initial begin
        s = "hello\r\n";
        $display("%s", s);
    end
endmodule
```

Saved to `test.sv`, and compiled with `iverilog -g2012 test.sv -o out`, and executed with `vvp out`.  The iverilog used is the latest commit to the master branch.

The program should have printed `hello`, but instead printed `hellor`.  It appears that \r is being translated to the regular letter "r", not the CR character (0x13).

